я, Великобритания, её отцу по имени Hélie Crevequer было 18 лет, а матери, которую звали Cecila de Kent, 17. Она вышла замуж за человека по имени Bertram de Criol около 1140 г. в местности сарр, кэнт, Англия. У них был по крайней мере 1 сын. Она умерла в 1207 г. в местности суттон, кэнт, Англия, Великобритания в возрасте 79 лет."},"sm":{"1128–1207":"1128–1207","1130–1177":"1130–1177","1118–1160":"1118–1160","1150–1227":"1150–1227","1110–1145":"1110–1145","1111–1170":"1111–1170","about 1150":"e tusa o le 1150","about 1140":"e tusa o le 1140","abt 1160":"e tusa o le 1160","1110":"1110","1130":"1130","1150":"1150","1160":"1160","1170":"1170","1118":"1118","1128":"1128","1227":"1227","1145":"1145","1111":"1111","1177":"1177","um 1127":"e tusa o le 1127","1207":"1207","Leeds Castle, Leeds, Kent, England":"Leeds, Kent, Egelani, United Kingdom","Sarre, Kent, England":"Sarre, Kent, Egelani","Sutton, Eastry, Kent, England":"Sutton, Kent, Egelani, United Kingdom","Ashburnham, Sussex, England":"Ashburnham, Sussex, Egelani","Leeds Castle, Kent, England":"Leeds, Kent, Egelani, United Kingdom"},"sk":{"1128–1207":"1128–1207","1130–1177":"1130–1177","1118–1160":"1118–1160","1150–1227":"1150–1227","1110–1145":"1110–1145","1111–1170":"1111–1170","about 1150":"okolo 1150","about 1140":"okolo 1140","abt 1160":"okolo 1160","1110":"1110","1130":"1130","1150":"1150","1160":"1160","1170":"1170","1118":"1118","1128":"1128","1227":"1227","1145":"1145","1111":"1111","1177":"1177","um 1127":"okolo 1127","1207":"1207","Leeds Castle, Leeds, Kent, England":"Leeds, Kent, Anglicko, Spojené kráľovstvo","Sarre, Kent, England":"Sarre, Kent, England","Sutton, Eastry, Kent, England":"Sutton, Kent, Anglicko, Spojené kráľovstvo","Ashburnham, Sussex, England":"Ashburnham, Sussex, England","Leeds Castle, Kent, England":"Leeds, Kent, Anglicko, Spojené kráľovstvo"},"es":{"1128–1207":"1128–1207","1130–1177":"1130–1177","1118–1160":"1118–1160","1150–1227":"1150–1227","1110–1145":"1110–1145","1111–1170":"1111–11